# Task API

A simple CRUD API built with FastAPI.

The API allows users to create, view, update, and delete tasks. It also includes a health-check endpoint and automatically generated Swagger documentation.

## Features

- Create a task
- List all tasks
- Get one task by ID
- Update a task
- Delete a task
- Input validation
- Proper HTTP status codes
- Swagger UI documentation

## Installation and Running

Install the required packages:

```bash
pip install fastapi uvicorn


